##### Sasson - Advanced Drupal Theming. #####

This is the directory for all your nodes templates.

Default node template can be found here :
https://api.drupal.org/api/drupal/modules%21node%21node.tpl.php/7

Template suggestions:
node--[type|nodeid].tpl.php

base template: node.tpl.php

Theme hook suggestions are made based on these factors, listed from the most
specific template to the least. Drupal will use the most specific template it finds:

node--nodeid.tpl.php
node--type.tpl.php
node.tpl.php
